  "summary": "Out-of-bounds Read in OpenCV",
  "details": "An issue was discovered in OpenCV before 3.4.7 and 4.x before 4.1.1 (OpenCV-Python before 3.4.7.28 and 4.x before 4.1.1.26). There is an out of bounds read in the function cv::predictOrdered\u003ccv::HaarEvaluator\u003e in modules/objdetect/src/cascadedetect.hpp, which leads to denial of service.",
